{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01T2FPnrkb63xhNE3vcxkuCj","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-21\n     2→\n     3→### 0-1-sprint-state-live-updates — verify (2026-03-21T07:55Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **Bug found and fixed:** `parseRalphStatus()` in `migration.ts` was missing the new `currentStory`, `currentPhase`, `lastAction`, `acProgress` fields added by this story. Migration test was failing. Fixed by adding null defaults to the return object.\n     6→- **Observability gap:** VictoriaLogs returned zero log events for all `codeharness progress` CLI invocations. The progress command doesn't emit structured logs.\n     7→\n     8→### 0-2-ralph-progress-display — verify (2026-03-21T08:00Z)\n     9→\n    10→- **Proof format issue:** AC3 initially reused evidence from AC2 without its own `bash` code block, causing `codeharness verify` to report 3/4 ACs. Fixed by adding a distinct bash block.\n    11→- **No BATS tests in container:** `ralph/tests/` not included in npm package. Verification relied on direct function invocation with mock data.\n    12→- **VictoriaLogs query syntax:** `_stream_id:*` pattern invalid for VictoriaLogs. Used `*` wildcard instead.\n    13→\n    14→### 0-3-run-command-dashboard — verify (2026-03-21T08:04Z)\n    15→\n    16→- **Minor format deviations:** Story specified checkmark/cross prefixes but implementation uses `[OK]`/`[FAIL]` tags. Functionally equivalent, passed verification.\n    17→- **Architecture difference:** Story specified `DashboardFormatter` class but implementation uses Ink React components. Same functionality, different design.\n    18→\n    19→### 0-5-1-stream-json-claude-driver — verify (2026-03-21T08:09Z)\n    20→\n    21→- Clean verification — all 4 ACs passed without issues.\n    22→\n    23→### 0-5-2-stream-event-parser — verify (2026-03-21T14:33Z)\n    24→\n    25→- **Non-standard status:** Sprint status had `verified` (not a valid status), story file said `in-progress`. Treated as `verifying`.\n    26→- **Unit-testable but not tagged:** Story is a pure function library with zero external effects but lacked `<!-- verification-tier: unit-testable -->` tag. Added it manually.\n    27→- **Parser not CLI-accessible:** `parseStreamLine()` is not exported from the main package bundle — tree-shaken out. Black-box Docker verification impossible. Used unit-testable verification path.\n    28→- **verify command contradiction:** `codeharness verify --story 0-5-2-stream-event-parser` returned `[FAIL] Proof quality check failed: 6/6 ACs verified` — reports FAIL but 6/6 ACs passed. Presentation bug.\n    29→- **Pre-commit gate:** `verification_run: false` in session_flags blocked commit. Had to update `.claude/codeharness.local.md` via sed.\n    30→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011ohxVSt43AbkaZDqYukGni","session_id":"3302fb5a-267f-479c-8444-7f3205e5b9bb","uuid":"e5f34e17-ca65-4c5a-90e2-9963143f9fae","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:35:21.273Z"}
